Third-party filter lists

Bundled `WKContentRuleList` JSON under Resources/ContentBlocker/ is
converted (build-time) from:

- EasyList and EasyPrivacy (https://easylist.to/)
  Copyright The EasyList authors
  https://easylist.to/pages/licence.html

- Fanboy's Cookie List (https://www.fanboy.co.nz/)
  Same family of licences as EasyList

- AdGuard filters (Base, Tracking, Social, Annoyances)
  https://adguard.com/ / https://filters.adtidy.org/
  See AdGuard filter licence terms for each list

Conversion uses AdGuard SafariConverterLib as an external build tool
(https://github.com/AdguardTeam/SafariConverterLib, GNU GPLv3).
That tool is not distributed or linked into Oriel; only the resulting
JSON rule data is shipped.

Script: Scripts/build_content_blocker.py
